korean: 오늘 좋은 일도 있고 걱정되는 일도 있어서 복잡했다.
기쁜 마음과 불안한 마음이 동시에 들었어.
감정이 너무 많아서 정리가 안 된다.
english: Today was complicated because there were good things and worrying things.
I felt happy and anxious at the same time.
There are so many emotions that I can't sort them out.
I need to think about them slowly, one by one.
